# =============================================================================
# HSalsa20 known-answer
#
# key   = 32 zero bytes
# input = 16 zero bytes
# Expected output (Python-verified against DJB spec):
#   351f86faa3b988468a850122b65b0ace
#   ce9c4826806aeee63de9c0da2bd7f91e
# =============================================================================

